The top 3 reasons to play Grand Theft Auto V (GTA 5): Premium Online Edition
Play as Michael De Santa, Franklin Clinton and Trevor Philips in the latest Grand Theft Auto experience.
Grand Theft Auto V: Premium Online Edition includes the full game, Grand Theft Auto Online and all content including The Doomsday Heist, Gunrunning, Smuggler’s Run, Bikers and much more.
Experience the award-winning Grand Theft Auto franchise and its take on modern, gangster culture.
About Grand Theft Auto V (GTA 5): Premium Online Edition
Switch between three characters as you attempt to pull off a series of heists.
Experience Grand Theft Auto V with stunning visuals running up to 4k resolution and 60 frames per second.
The PC version of Grand Theft Auto V features First Person Mode, giving players a brand new experience of Los Santos from an entirely new perspective.
Grand Theft Auto V for PC also includes the Rockstar Editor, so you can quickly and easily capture, edit and share game footage.

fields.name: GOD OF WAR PS4
fields.description:
God of War is the 8th installment of the God of War series and is the sequel to God of War III.

A new adventure awaits, and this time it is centered on Norse mythology, not unlike the previous God of War games that are loosely based on Greek mythology.
It has been years since Kratos took vengeance on the Greek gods. He was able to survive the final encounter with his father Zeus, however, he now lives in the land of the Norse gods with his son Atreus.
His newfound role as a father figure to his son will have him protecting, as well as teaching, his son the ropes of survival.
This time around, Kratos will not have his double-chained blades but will instead wield a magical battle ax called the Leviathan Axe.
This new installment is also played single-player only with Atreus helping Kratos from time to time.

fields.name: MINECRAFT XBOX ONE
fields.description:
The top 3 reasons to play Minecraft
- Quite simply, Minecraft is a game about placing blocks. What you create, and the adventures you go on are up to you!
- Minecraft is virtually limitless. The game’s Lego-like world is just perfect for creativity, experimentation, and modding.
- Minecraft is continually updated by its developer, and thousands of mods are available from the game's active community!


About Minecraft
Experience one of the most popular and best-selling games of all time.
Minecraft is virtually limitless. The game’s Lego-like world is just perfect for creativity, experimentation, and modding.
Let your imagination run wild in creative mode, or fend off dangerous mods in survival mode!
Explore a variety of randomly generated biomes.
Enjoy cross-platform play between Windows 10, Xbox One, and other compatible devices.
Customize your game. The variety and types of mods currently available are nearly limitless

fields.name: SUPER SMASH BROS. ULTIMATE SWITCH
fields.description:
The top 3 reasons to play Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Switch
- This is the biggest and most ambitious Super Smash Bros. game ever made. Icons from throughout the Nintendo universe have gathered for the ultimate showdown!
- From Pikachu to Bayonetta, 74 different fighters await your challenge (plus even more with DLC)!
- Every character in SSBU has a devastating Final Smash that’s totally unique. Get in the game and try them out to find your favorite!

About Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Switch
Prepare for Ultimate brawls with an Ultimate lineup of Nintendo gaming icons!
Brand new items hold the key to victory in Super Smash Bros. Ultimate; grab them before your opponent does!
SSBU features over 100 different fighting stages-- including arenas from previous Smash Bros. games that have been powered up!
Over 800 new music tracks are included in Super Smash Bros. Ultimate to keep your battles fresh, fun, and exciting!.
